(6, 'medium', 'What is hybrid inheritance?', 'Combination of more than one inheritance type', 'Only single inheritance', 'No inheritance', 'Only multilevel inheritance', 'Combination of more than one inheritance type', 'Hybrid inheritance mixes different inheritance patterns.'),
